snippet.title: “A year in the life of Britain’s youngest transgender children” - BBC News

localized.description:
Last year, the Victoria Derbyshire programme met two children who were born as boys but have been living as girls. Lily and Jessica are now 7 and 9 and they’ve been telling Victoria how they’ve transitioned at school and at home.
